headline: C40 and Carrier Collaborate to Help Cities Tackle Extreme Heat and Enhance Climate Resilience
summary: C40 Cities, the global network of nearly 100 cities united to confront the climate crisis, has collaborated with Carrier, global leader in intelligent climate and energy solutions, to help cities adapt to dramatically changing global temperatures.
